00:58:03,690 --> 00:58:06,250
Take a little

923
00:58:06,330 --> 00:58:08,770
And let your poor heart

924
00:58:08,810 --> 00:58:11,490
Break a little

925
00:58:11,530 --> 00:58:14,210
That's the story of

